data.description: This home offers four spacious bedrooms upstairs, providing ample room for family and guests. The primary suite is a sanctuary in itself, complete with a private ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet. The addition bathrooms are equally comfortable and tastefully designed, ensuring that everyone has their own personal haven. This kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, boasting a modern design. For more information contact Annie Wedgewood with Altitude Real Estate at 307-705-6783,The backyard of 3700 Madison is truly a haven for relaxation and entertainment. Step outside onto the expansive deck and patio, perfect for hosting barbecues or simply enjoying a morning coffee while soaking in the picturesque views. The fully fenced yard provides a safe space for children and pets to play, while mature trees offer shade and privacy. Conveniently located near parks, schools, and shopping centers, this property embodies the essence of comfortable and luxurious living. With it's elegant design, functional layout, and stunning surroundings, this property is truly a place you can call home. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this exceptional property in Rock Springs, Wyoming. Schedule a visit today and fall in love with the beauty and charm of 3700 Madison.
